Titolo: Multiplayer BattleTech 3025

Anno: 2001

Descrizione: Multiplayer BattleTech: 3025 is a PC MMORPG developed by Kesmai during the same period as Microsoft's MechWarrior 4: Vengeance.  The game occupies the fictional 31st century universe of BattleTech and focuses centrally on the large robotic war machines called BattleMechs ('Mechs) and the individuals who pilot them.  The game was released as a beta in 2001 and shut down with little explanation on December 6, 2001.